Needed for 64 bit systems:
--------------------------
$ sudo apt-get install libc6:i386 libx11-6:i386 libxext6:i386 libstdc++6:i386 libexpat1:i386

Change permission of tinybldlin.py:
-----------------------------------
Assuming the you have followed the instruction on creating the workspace, type the following command
$ chmod +x ~/ECEP/Microcontrollers/Tools/tinybldlin/src/tinybldlin.py
